flowchart TD

A[Enter Home Page] --> B[Select Self Check-in]

B --> C{Do you have an account?}

C -->|Yes| D[Log in]
C -->|No| E[Choose Check-in Method]

E --> F[Enter Email or Reservation ID]

D --> G[Fetch Reservation Data]
F --> G

G --> H[Display Reservation Details]

H --> I[Select Room]

I --> J[Fill Check-in Form]

J --> K[Upload ID / Identity Verification]

K --> L[Confirm Check-in]

L --> M[Update Reservation Status to Checked-in]

M --> N[Show Check-in Confirmation]
